{"about_the_game":"Dead Mire is a unique atmospheric fast-paced endless wave zombie gore fest.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406730/extras/ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converted.gif?t=1707523543\" /><br><br>Ammo is scarce so you must use it tactically to dispose of as many zombies as you can with as few shots as possible. You are armed with a double barrel shotgun and you can switch between buckshot, birdshot and slugs which you must choose between wisely to maximize your damage output in any given situation.<br><br>Birdshot gives you a very wide cone but short range, ideal for taking out swarms of zombies grouping you. <br>Slugs have long range and will pass through objects and other zombies but travels in a narrow line, best used when you line up zombies behind one another.<br>Buckshot is a balance between range and width; your bread and butter for taking out zombies along with barrels and crates.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406730/extras/ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converted__1_.gif?t=1707523543\" /><br><br>Make use of portals and bullet time to extend and break up shots, killing more zombies in a single shot. Ammo and health potions spawn from broken barrels and crates which can also be destroyed with teleported shots, traps and dynamite, maximizing your ammo conservation.<br><br>Compete against other players on the Steam leaderboard to see who can kill the most zombies before they die or run out of ammunition!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406730/extras/download__4___1_.png?t=1707523543\" />","achievements":{"total":0},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406730/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1707523543","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406730/page.bg.jpg?t=1707